  "category": "JavaScript",
  "category_int": 10,
  "feature_notes": "Firefox never ship it. \nSafari ship the removing getters in \nSafari 15.4 Release Notes\nReleased March 14, 2022 — Version 15.4 (17613.1.17)\nhttps://developer.apple.com/documentation/safari-release-notes/safari-15_4-release-notes\n\nand removed these getters in \nSafari 17 Release Notes\nReleased September 18, 2023 — Version 17 (19616.1.27)\nhttps://developer.apple.com/documentation/safari-release-notes/safari-17-release-notes\n\"Updated Intl.Locale to replace info getters with individual get… methods. (105570888)\" ",
